reviews.review_text: Weir's voice is shot Good set list, espescially the second set (besides Corrina), but Weir's voice is totally shot. It makes the Weir tunes unlistenable!

Dandy These Denver shows were the first shows back after Jerry's health hit the skids that fall...the heads all showed up in denver despite foul weather to watch the band re-launch itself.  I have read other reviews of this show where people have nothing good to say about the first set.  However, the whole show was a dandy to attend.  The peggy-o in the first set was simply beautiful.
